The AI solution i propose is a Mathematics AI assistant that supports learners at primary, secondary and university level. 
This AI tool will provide step by step guidance on maths problems, adapting to each student's learning pace. This aligns with the Education 
Department. It will benefit teachers and learners as it improves quality access to quality math education especially for those 
with limited resources where expert tutors may not be available. 

This AI tool icludes:*
The AI will offer natural langauge prossessing  to understand and interpret maths questions presented by students in the form of image, text, 
audio, video and compressed file.
This system will also adapt to other interactions when solving a problem.

